"1 cup chopped walnut pieces","1 pound plus 3 oz. bacon, chopped","3/4 cup packed light brown sugar","1/2 teaspoon red chile flakes","1 cup butter, melted, foam skimmed","1  pkg. frozen filo dough (1 lb., sheets about 13 in. by 17 in.), thawed","1 cup (12 oz.) orange marmalade, preferably thin-cut, such as Bonne Maman","1/4 cup orange-flavored liqueur, such as Cointreau"